    <li>Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://twitter.com/privacy</a></li>
    <li>Instagram: <a href="http://instagram.com/about/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://instagram.com/about/legal/privacy/</a></li>
    <li>YouTube: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/intl/es/about/policies/#community-guidelines" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.youtube.com/intl/es/about/policies/</a></li>
  </ul>

